snippet.title: Who's gonna pop the balloon first?
snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE & ADOPT A KATANA WITH THE LINK IN BIO!! 

If you love katana unboxing, then you'll love this. See the Katanas slice in action as satisfying as ASMR! These aren't rusted katanas! Sword-making, blacksmithing, knife making, and katana making are Mini Katana's passions! If you love anime like One Piece, Naruto, Demon Slayer, Attack on Titan, Miira No Kaikata, Mugen Train, Jujutsu Kaisen, sword art online abridged, slice of life anime, chainsaw man vs katana, afro samurai and are excited about the Swordsmith arc, you're gonna love our ninja weapons! Mini Katana is the founding titan of katana making, knife making, and the mini katana keychain. Learn how to draw a katana and how to make kunai like Naruto. We are the last samurai. We love Japanese anime, Japanese history, Japanese lofi, Japanese movies, and Japanese songs. Subscribe to watch mini katana unboxing, how to make a katana with cardboard and with paper, and more!  The Mini Katana Store is committed to high quality carbon steel blades and giving you slice of life looks as we try not to laugh challenge. Trust, Mini Katana knows how to make kunai and how to make a sword!

snippet.title: The World's Highest Security Prison: CECOT (The most evil are kept here)
snippet.description:
Welcome to CECOT, the worldâ€™s largest prison by capacity in El Salvador which was constructed to imprison the worst of the worst. 
Subscribe â–º https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
Those who enter this prison are destined to never leave here. This is the worldâ€™s strictest and largest mega prison. It has a capacity of 40,000. 
Built in 2022, this massive prison is made up of eight separate modules spread over 410 acres of land. Each pair of modules is enclosed by two separate 3-meter-high walls with razor wire. The entire facility is surrounded by a towering 9-meter-high wall with a 3-meter-high electric fence carrying 15,000 volts. Nineteen watchtowers are ensuring nothing escapes notice. The entire design doesnâ€™t just prevent escape, it erases the very idea of it.

Also, I conducted an exclusive interview with one of the inmates, who is 41 years old.  In this interview, he reveals what life inside CECOT is really like. 

Our team that worked in this project: https://docs.google.com/document/d/13G3oENBE-jGeyjoY50xmb3DyiGeUiSMRIZoQfOF1lGQ/edit?tab=t.0

"Rediscovery" Series â–º https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL40Eh9f0PRRXcCkyKxrtRvE3tbmcKYvHr

Visiting the Fattest, Most Cigarette-Addicted and Least Visited Country ğŸ‡³ğŸ‡· â–º https://youtu.be/eUJgq9HerDQ
Visiting the World's Hottest Place (70Â°C, 159Â°F) LUT DESERT â–º https://youtu.be/NhyDkHaUC8U
Visiting the MOST AIR POLLUTED CITY in the World (Dust Hell) â–º https://youtu.be/zC4saZg6sG0
Visiting the COLDEST CITY in the World (-71Â°C, -96Â°F) YAKUTSK / YAKUTIA â–º https://youtu.be/Fz4ZMLsPzqM
8 Crazy Experiments at -55Â°C, -67Â°F (The coldest city in the World: Yakutsk) â–º https://youtu.be/ExoOL2lwlWE
World's Poorest Country "Burundi" (I canâ€™t forget the things I saw) â–º https://youtu.be/n0gFsHf9cIw

My name is Ruhi Ã‡enet, I'm an independent documentary maker. I go to unique places or meet unique people and investigate or analyze them with a unique approach. My motto is "curiosity is the best guide". Join me, let's learn something different...

hi.title: Duniya Ki Sabse Jyada High Security Wali Jail: CECOT (Yahan sabse bade shaitaan band hain)
hi.description:
CECOT mein aapka swagat hai, jo El Salvador mein duniya ki sabse badi jail hai, jise sabse khatarnak apradhiyon ko kaid karne ke liye banaya gaya tha.

Sadasyata lein â–º https://goo.gl/mki8tn

Is jail mein pravesh karne wale log kabhi yahaan se baahar nahin nikal paate. Yah duniya ki sabse sakht aur sabse badi mega jail hai, jismein 40,000 kaidiyon ki kshamata hai.

2022 mein nirmit, yah vishal jail 410 ekad bhoomi par faile aath alag-alag modules se bani hai. Pratyek module jodi razor wire se surakshit do alag-alag 3-meter oonchi deewaron se ghiri hui hai. Poori suvidha 9 meter oonchi deewaar se ghiri hui hai, jismein 15,000 volt ki 3-meter oonchi bijli ki baadh hai. Unnees watchtower yah sunishchit kar rahe hain ki koi bhi cheez nazar se na chhute. Poora design na keval bhaagne se rokta hai, balki bhaagne ke vichar ko hi mita deta hai.

Iske alawa, maine 41 varshiya ek kaidi se ek vishesh saakshatkaar liya. Is saakshatkaar mein, unhone bataya ki CECOT ke andar ka jeevan vastav mein kaisa hai.

id.title: Penjara Dengan Keamanan Tertinggi di Dunia: CECOT (Para Iblis ditahan di sini)
id.description:
Selamat datang di CECOT, penjara terbesar di dunia berdasarkan kapasitas di El Salvador yang dibangun untuk memenjarakan yang terburuk dari yang terburuk.
Berlangganan â–º https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
Mereka yang masuk penjara ini ditakdirkan untuk tidak pernah keluar dari sini. Ini adalah penjara mega yang paling ketat dan terbesar di dunia. Kapasitasnya 40.000.
Dibangun pada tahun 2022, penjara besar ini terdiri dari delapan modul terpisah yang tersebar di lahan seluas 410 hektar. Setiap pasang modul dikelilingi oleh dua dinding terpisah setinggi 3 meter dengan kawat berduri. Seluruh fasilitas dikelilingi oleh tembok setinggi 9 meter dengan pagar listrik setinggi 3 meter yang membawa 15.000 volt. Sembilan belas menara pengawas memastikan tidak ada yang luput dari perhatian. Seluruh desain tidak hanya mencegah pelarian, tetapi juga menghapus gagasan tentang pelarian.

Saya juga melakukan wawancara eksklusif dengan salah satu narapidana, yang berusia 41 tahun. Dalam wawancara ini, ia mengungkapkan seperti apa sebenarnya kehidupan di dalam CECOT.

en.title: The World's Highest Security Prison: CECOT (The most evil are kept here)
en.description:
Welcome to CECOT, the worldâ€™s largest prison by capacity in El Salvador which was constructed to imprison the worst of the worst. 
Subscribe â–º https://goo.gl/MKi8tn
Those who enter this prison are destined to never leave here. This is the worldâ€™s strictest and largest mega prison. It has a capacity of 40,000. 
Built in 2022, this massive prison is made up of eight separate modules spread over 410 acres of land. Each pair of modules is enclosed by two separate 3-meter-high walls with razor wire. The entire facility is surrounded by a towering 9-meter-high wall with a 3-meter-high electric fence carrying 15,000 volts. Nineteen watchtowers are ensuring nothing escapes notice. The entire design doesnâ€™t just prevent escape, it erases the very idea of it.

Also, I conducted an exclusive interview with one of the inmates, who is 41 years old.  In this interview, he reveals what life inside CECOT is really like. 

Our team that worked in this project: https://docs.google.com/document/d/13G3oENBE-jGeyjoY50xmb3DyiGeUiSMRIZoQfOF1lGQ/edit?tab=t.0

"Rediscovery" Series â–º https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL40Eh9f0PRRXcCkyKxrtRvE3tbmcKYvHr

Visiting the MOST AIR POLLUTED CITY in the World (Dust Hell) â–º https://youtu.be/zC4saZg6sG0
Visiting the COLDEST CITY in the World (-71Â°C, -96Â°F) YAKUTSK / YAKUTIA â–º https://youtu.be/Fz4ZMLsPzqM
8 Crazy Experiments at -55Â°C, -67Â°F (The coldest city in the World: Yakutsk) â–º https://youtu.be/ExoOL2lwlWE
World's Poorest Country "Burundi" (I canâ€™t forget the things I saw) â–º https://youtu.be/n0gFsHf9cIw
